<content>
    
    <para id="id1166578306812">In the pre-credit sequence of the 1965 film <emphasis effect="italics">Thunderball</emphasis>, James Bond 007 (played by Sean Connery) uses a Jetpack to escape from two gunmen after killing Jacques Bouvar, SPECTRE Agent No. 6 (<link target-id="id1166580328345"/>). The Jetpack was also used in the <emphasis effect="italics">Thunderball</emphasis> posters, being the "Look Up" part of the "Look Up! Look Down! Look Out!" tagline (<link target-id="id1166610011451"/>). The Jetpack returned in 2002 in <emphasis effect="italics">Die Another Day</emphasis> (in which Pierce Brosnan played Bond) in the Q scene that showcased many other classic gadgets from previous Bond films. </para>


